                My family, my children and grandchildren, brothers and sister, have just helped me so much and buoyed my spirit in so many ways and strengthened me through letters, email, cards, pictures, and the spiritual help that I have from the scriptures, my patriarchal blessing, and from friends here in the mission, and especially being able to serve at the same time as six missionary grandchildren. <br /><br />

